    "passives": {
      "DefeatAnEnemyPassiveARizetteBrave": {
        "id": "DefeatAnEnemyPassiveARizetteBrave",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Instant Link",
          "description": "This unit starts with Rizette's Link. When this unit enters battle it grants Rizette's Link to another random non-conjured ally that does not have a Link already. Then that ally and this unit have the TU costs for all of their skills reduced by 30% (This will overwrite the effects of other Quicken skills), and are granted a Sleep Ward, Stun Ward, Poison Ward and Instant Death Ward.\n\nA unit with Rizette's Link has these effects:\n\nEach time an ally with Rizette's Link gets the turn, this unit will be healed for 50% of its max HP.\n\nThis unit has 0.25x of their original Attack added to their Attack while they are not Enraged. This increase will stack with other Attack increases (e.g. 1.5x + 0.25x => 1.75x total).\n\nWhen this unit defeats an enemy with an attack, if the defeated enemy is:\n- Fire or Light, 2 random non-sleeping enemies gain the Sleep status effect for 100TU, even if they have already slept while on the battlefield.\n- Storm or Earth, 2 random non-burning enemies gain the Lethal Poison status effect.\n- Water or Dark, 2 random enemies that have a current TU of 50 or less are stunned for 100TU.\nThese effects may trigger before or after other effects.\n\nThis Link is removed if this unit or the unit that granted it leaves the battlefield. This unit cannot gain other Links.\n\nLethal Poison will overwrite other status effects, lasts 999 TU, cannot be overwritten by status effects other than Burn or Stealth, and cannot be Purified. Lethal Poison deals 2 times the damage of normal Poison, and ignores passive skills or effects of active skills that would prevent the target from being defeated, other than those which specifically prevent defeat from Poison or non-attack damage. Lethal Poison cannot apply to Burning or Boss units."
        }
      },
      "DualBondPassiveARizetteBrave": {
        "id": "DualBondPassiveARizetteBrave",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Cerulean Valkyrie",
          "description": "If this unit would be defeated by an enemy attack or a status effect while having more than 1 HP, it instead survives with 1 HP.\n\nThis unit cannot be sent to the reinforcements from the battlefield.\n\nThis unit's attacks will not wake sleeping enemies and heal this unit for 100% of total damage dealt.\n\nThis unit has 80% damage reduction from attacks for 100TU. Afterwards this unit has 40% damage reduction instead.\n\nEach time an ally with Rizette's Link gets the turn, this unit will be Purified at the end of the turn.\n\nThis unit has Sleep immunity and Stun immunity. These immunity effects are removed from this unit if this is the only ally on the battlefield with Rizette's Link (these immunity effects cannot be restored)."
        }
      },
